text:
Hi <!subteam^S06HNNE4YQ0|@team>!! This fall we have some awesome *outreach workshops* lined up for the Ithaca community :mega:
Thank you so much for sending in your availability earlier this year with times you're able to help volunteer - we tried our best to accommodate schedules as well as stay within the working hours of our partners!

We are excited to collaborate with the *Tompkins County Public Library*:house_with_garden: in holding two workshops for older adults!! Please signup using this <https://forms.gle/WmtBn8BT1jxysNYu9|form> to help volunteer at the event! It will be an amazing opportunity to meet new people and enrich your life:yay: We will *cap volunteers at 5 per event* so get your submissions in!

:point_right::skin-tone-2:Workshop #1: Digital Technology & Scams Seminar, *October 20th, 1:30-3pm*
:point_right::skin-tone-2:Workshop #2: Technology 101 Seminar, *November 10th, 1:30-3pm*

Also BIG shoutout to <@U08E3UNQDTM> for helping create the beautiful graphics (attached here) for these workshops! Feel free to share with any group you know who might be interested in attending :blush:
Let me know if you have questions!!
